But I guarantee you,
this guy,

59:10.730 --> 59:13.600
he didn't kill
anybody yesterday.

59:13.700 --> 59:15.168
And why is that?

59:15.268 --> 59:18.137
Because he's been
dead at least a week.

59:18.237 --> 59:21.574
Apparent self-inflicted
gun wound into the mouth.

59:21.674 --> 59:23.142
Did leave a note, though.

59:23.242 --> 59:27.247
Says for Katrina,
take all of my money

59:27.347 --> 59:29.582
