- <i>Yes, we can now confirm...</i>
<i>- Shit!</i>

01:10:09.021 --> 01:10:11.190
<i>The leaked footage is,</i>
<i>in fact, genuine.</i>

01:10:11.290 --> 01:10:13.559
<i>It's being called</i>
<i>a snuff film.</i>

01:10:13.659 --> 01:10:16.829
<i>And others on the web are</i>
<i>calling it an instant classic.</i>

01:10:16.929 --> 01:10:18.764
<i>What we know for sure</i>
<i>is that this video</i>

01:10:18.864 --> 01:10:21.800
<i>has gone viral,</i>
